history.content: (This is eecs 101 and it's been asked before but) a good place for these questions is the "mathematics" group under the big Berkeley group because one of the advisors (Jennifer Sixt) is in that group. Off the top of my head Jennifer and Thomas Brown are good people to contact. Also Ana Renteria. You can find their emails with a simple google search.
